EX-OR Technique

Ex-Or Ing is a technique to solve problems like find duplicate in array or find unique value
in array or permutation sum in codility (Lession 4: Counting Elements - Perm Check)
https://app.codility.com/demo/results/trainingVUTWTE-F6T/

When you ex-or number with itself you get value as 0
When you ex-or number with some different number you get a non zero value

Think about this technique if you get above problems in coding test